results.name: Sum of the divisors of n that are not divisible by 10.
link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
program: print([sum([i for i in divisors(n) if i%10]) for n in range(1, 101)]) # _Indranil Ghosh_, Mar 25 2017
xref: Cf. Sum of the divisors of n that are not divisible by k: A046913 (k=3), A046897 (k=4), A116073 (k=5), A284326 (k=6), A113957 (k=7), A284341 (k=8), A116607 (k=9), this sequence (k=10).
